  <h1 style="font-size:90px;color:#fff;margin:0;letter-spacing:8px;animation:fadeUp 1s ease both;animation-delay:1s;opacity:0;text-shadow:0 0 60px rgba(201,168,76,0.3);">AURORA</h1>
